    "actor_description": "My mind fills up faster than it can empty. Thoughts stack, priorities blur, and everything starts arriving with the same sharp insistence. I can feel my body trying to sprint while my attention keeps snagging—breath quick, shoulders tight, jaw set. I want to force the moment to behave, and the strain shows in how little room I have left for anything else.",
